        <item>
            <title>百度发表文心大模型 4.0　「与 GPT-4 相比毫不逊色」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/17/baidu-6/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=baidu-6</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/17/baidu-6/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[毛]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 07:30:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199704</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>百度创办人、行政总裁李彦宏今（17 日）宣布文心大模型 4.0 正式发布。他表示，文心大模型 4.0 是迄今为止最强大的文心大模型，综合水准与 GPT-4 相比毫不逊色。</p><p>李彦宏指出，文心大模型 4.0 在理解、生成、逻辑和记忆能力上都有明显提升，亦在会场内示范各个文心大模型 4.0 的新功能。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199706" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.44.26-PM-694x339.png" alt="" width="694" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.44.26-PM-694x339.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.44.26-PM-1280x626.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.44.26-PM-768x376.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.44.26-PM-1536x751.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.44.26-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在生成能力方面，文心大模型 4.0 可透过网络上的内容结合用户的指令，生成广告海报、文案，甚至营销影片。李彦宏表示，大模型 4.0 成功实现「一个人就成为一支 AI 营销队伍」，并宣布百度已基于这项功能推出 AIGC 行销创意平台擎舵。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199708" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.59.40-PM-694x404.png" alt="" width="694" height="404" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.59.40-PM-694x404.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.59.40-PM-1280x745.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.59.40-PM-768x447.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.59.40-PM-1536x895.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-17-at-2.59.40-PM.png 1542w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>李彦宏亦透过让文心大模型 4.0 做数学题、总结知识点的方式展现期逻辑能力。同时使用文心大模型 4.0 撰写约数千字的武侠小说，透过其角色设定、情节展现大模型的纪历能力等等。</p><p>李彦宏表示，以上的演示体现出文心大模型 4.0 在 4 大能力上的准备，而这些能力是一切 AI 原生应用程式赖以生存的基础。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/940/940208.htm">快科技</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
