            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199422</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 2018 年以改编自 Marvel 英雄漫画所推出的动作游戏推出的《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman》其流畅动作游戏玩法与开放式地图大受好评，继而在 2020 年推出续集外传作品《Marvel&#8217;s Spider-Man: Miles Morales》来使用黑蜘蛛及特殊能力。直到 2023 年让故事回到正传，推出游戏《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》让前两集主角再度携手合作保护纽约家园的故事，正当大家期待新作品的时候然而这次感谢 PlayStation 提供的评测用游戏可以优先为 Unwire 读者进行评测。《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》于 2023 年 10 月 20 日正式发售，并只有 Playstation 5 平台才能游玩。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199486 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-6-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲第二集画面大幅提升</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_GameplayReveal_MilesCombat_4K_Legal_2023-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲战斗方式也是改变不少</p><h2>面对现实与挑战，双主角的成长纪录</h2><p>《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》的故事设定是上集《Miles Morales》的九个月后，渡过不少人生历练之后终于回归正常生活，但是世事岂能如常往往都有不同的危机，在双主角互相重新审视自己的同时，一个接一个的强大反派都影响著两位成为了成长的一部份。如果没有游玩前两集的玩家也不用担心游戏会跟不上进度，也建议多花时间先观看「剧情回顾」来对游戏中的蜘蛛侠有一定认识。在游戏整体的剧情都跟以往一样十分流畅，如果是冲著剧情的部份玩家不用担心，光是序章的部份就足以好比在看一场电影。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199496 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-11-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲要面对现实的困难</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Heroes_4K_Legal-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这次双主角故事</p><h2>史诗式的对战，强大的敌人登场</h2><p>要说到《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 》系列除了强大的游戏剧情外，就是在游戏中出现的强大敌人。而这次游戏所铺排出场的敌人，都是有著不同的个人特色霸气登场，而登场的敌人除了曾在 Trailer 出现的几个敌人外，还有更多极具危险的敌人潜伏著等待玩家大驾光临。在游戏中每个敌人登场都会给玩家一大挑战，就像序章出现的沙人，所带给纽约市的变化与及留下后续事件让故事延续下去。随著故事开放玩家定能体验第 2 集所带来的敌人，假若玩家有留意蜘蛛侠漫画一定能体验游戏带来的诚意。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199490 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_LizardGrowl_4k_Legal_2023-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Trailer 出现过的蜥蜴人</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲序章沙人就充满惊喜</p><h2>更大的地图，更多的任务</h2><p>比较于前作地图只有纽约曼哈顿岛之外，《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》还加入东河彼岸的布鲁克林区与皇后区，相比前作差不多大了两倍，而且区域之间地方差异大玩家会体验当中的文化。那当然地图也是采用开放式无缝地图，而越大的地图就有更多的任务等著玩家挑战，像上集一样除了会有触发任务外，也可以扫描附近区域来取得资讯，今集更有著另一个功能「友善的邻家蜘蛛人 APP」，玩家可以接受随机任务完成后来获得经验值。值得注意与上集相若也是需要完成一些谜题才能开放区域，所以玩家可以优先先打开地图。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199484 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-8-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今集地图超大</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_TimeSquare-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲游戏中时代广场</p><h2>拳拳到肉的表现，动作流畅极佳</h2><p>《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》保留了最原始最心动的动作效果，假若有游玩以前作品的玩家在操作上必定能很快上手，射蜘蛛网，轻攻击，闪避等等的操作仍然是一样的，如没玩过的玩家也只需要按著教学慢慢操作即可。今集玩家可以在双角色间切换操作，使用超能力的黑蜘蛛特效上会比较浮夸一点，而蜘蛛侠则是以物理一拳拳运用战衣打倒敌人，在战斗其间更有著慢动作与及各种动画的配合，使得战斗更流畅更刺激。今集也会大玩合作攻击，当然效果如何就等玩家自行慢慢发掘。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199492 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Preview_WallKick_4k_Legal_2023-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲游戏动作流畅度很高</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199487" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-4-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这次还有联合攻击</p><h2>重新设计的战斗系统，平衡战斗恰到好处</h2><p>这次《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》更改了不少的战斗系统，首先是不能再像以往一样所有攻击仅靠著回避功能去躲开敌人攻击，而是新增了另一种重攻击需要利用新功能「挡格」再化解攻击，这样玩家就要更留意敌人的变化采取措施。而另一方面蜘蛛侠的特殊技能再不是透过技能树或者连技使用出来，而是随著游戏进度装备技能只需透过 L1 加上右边四键使出强力攻击，不过这些技能都是有冷却时间，所以在运用的部份还是多多注意。这样变了战斗过程不会因技能太强大而草草了事，玩家就可以专心动作的部份。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199481 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-5-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲技能都会有冷却时间</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Attack_4K_Legal-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲游戏战斗平衡</p><h2>效能最佳化，让游戏推上另一个高度</h2><p>作为 Sony 旗下大作当然将游戏在 PS5 下发挥至最大效能，除了画质几乎是极限表现外，还有手制的触觉回馈，在不同环境下会有不同的震动与压力让玩家更有感觉。而游戏支援 Tempest 3D AudioTech 功能，假若有比较好的耳机或家庭音响记得感受一下那种澎湃的临场感觉。不论在画面上甚至是蜘蛛侠衣的细致位，在 SSD 下都能体验到真实又快速的冒险。值得一提的是《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》除了支援 HDR 与图形模式外，还支援了 120hz 及 VRR 「无上限」功能，对于拥有高阶电视的玩家在游戏下就更爽了。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199483 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-3-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲提起 120hz 跟 VRR</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-10-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲拥有高阶电视的玩家有更好的体验</p><h2>总结：绝对是今年最佳年度游戏名单之一</h2><p>《Marvel&#8217;s Spiderman 2》将真正次世代的画面与效能带出来的作品，在实际游玩的时候从画面完全感受到所带来的超美质感，在建筑物上或者一些特效火花上都有著超高水准的显示。其故事所传递的方式有深度又有意议，而且有游戏中的影片与真实游戏的运镜真的是超惊叹作品的完成度。光在纽约摆荡滑翔在城市就能体验邻居蜘蛛侠的生活。在如此高水准的作品下作为喜欢 Marvel 或是动作游戏的玩家，是值得推荐冲首发来支持一下。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199482 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲序章就可以体验游戏效能</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199485" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/M2M-7-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今集亦有技能树系统</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199489" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_DDE_20thCentury_4K_2023-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这次亦有多款战衣</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1199498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MSM2_Reveal_Venom_4K_Legal-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Venom 成为游戏一大关键</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
